
Menu:
- Press ESC to quit (a swell option).
- Press Space to play:
	- Move with WASD and use the mouse to pan.
	- Mouse wheel switches between 1st and 3rd person.
	- Left click to delete a selected block. Right click to place a block.
	- Avoid the enemies which will teleport you back to the start!
	- Press ESC to go back to the menu (be sure to wait at menu if you want to play again).
